{"tid":883590,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人帶過小露寶睇醫生？","createTime":"2018-10-31T03:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T19:12:05.000Z","uid":144540,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bc76f05dac863106ee5e103e4029798e729dee9c","tid":883590,"uid":144540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T03:06:42.000Z","msg":"我隻小露寶養左1年4個月，呢幾日佢身體好似抽畜咁，一下一下抖動，唔知係唔係肺部有問題，又冇咩食野，柯得一兩粒屎，所以想帶佢睇醫生。但係小露寶出名細膽，平時想同佢互動會都會驚，好容易被嚇，帶佢落街睇醫生會唔會令佢受驚病情更嚴重？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有帶小露寶去睇醫生既經驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514d21535dc1da55f8976ddb729ca1559ab968f7","tid":883590,"uid":196077,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T03:07:25.000Z","msg":"小老母"},{"pid":"28c3cf53e925a110368625ec4cd665bc18bffc15","tid":883590,"uid":65887,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.ecfoto.net/ericsfoto/22000000058041/wOkL6PrpPXLwWrtnMNqIRQ_S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.ecfoto.net%2Fericsfoto%2F22000000058041%2FwOkL6PrpPXLwWrtnMNqIRQ_S.jpg&h=be1abfac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24dc13d7201552b6b4e4564d46fac1c3d2de635d","tid":883590,"uid":81995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"小露寶係乜黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5378618844a9b1d019003229280c9a843a010a53","tid":883590,"uid":217954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"倉鼠係咁上下壽命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前帶過去睇<br />\n但無乜用"},{"pid":"06a3cee568233ef9e5ef63680e60e4284fa1e76b","tid":883590,"uid":60911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"但佢 屌人老母<img 